name: PepePunks DAO
description: PepePunks are more than just digital art. PepePunks are a movement. A protest against the culture vultures that say WAGMI but leave their fellow degens in the dust, holding the bag. Together, we can use our voices & skills to enact change in the Web3 space that we call home. We will show them what it looks like when people stop fighting and start working together.
